title: AQUA (Only) Auto-Compounding Vault
body:
We want to launch a new AQUA only vault, that will auto-compound all of the AQUA you earn for you to help maximize your APY.

Here's the details of the new auto-compounded AQUA vault we're proposing:

2.5% Performance Fee
0.1% Withdraw Fee
If this passes we will be removing the current AQUA vault (non auto-compounding) so that we just have the auto-compounding AQUA Vault.
